---
const word1 = "Carceral";
const definition1 =
  "Increasingly, the term is used to describe systems of social control that resemble or extend the reach of traditional prisons.";
const word2 = "Indolence";
const definition2 =
  "Avoidance of activity or exertion; laziness.";
const word3 = "Polymath";
const definition3 = "A person with wide-ranging knowledge or learning.";
const word4 = "Prosody";
const definition4 =
  "In linguistics, it refers to the patterns of stress and intonation in a language.";
---

<section id="current-episode">
  <div
    class="mx-auto w-full lg:px-24 max-w-7xl md:px-12 items-center px-8 py-24 scroll-mt-12"
  >
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-x-6 lg:gap-x-12">
      <div>
        <p
          class="text-4xl tracking-tight font-medium text-black text-center mb-8"
        >
          Current word list
        </p>
        <div class="bg-accent-50 mb-4">
          <div
            x-data="{ activeAccordion: '', setActiveAccordion(id) { this.activeAccordion = (this.activeAccordion == id) ? '' : id } }"
            class="relative w-full mx-auto font-normal"
          >
            <div
              x-data="{ id: $id('accordion') }"
              :class="{ 'text-black': activeAccordion==id, 'text-accent-900 hover:text-accent-600': activeAccordion!=id }"
              class="cursor-pointer group text-black"
            >
              <button
                @click="setActiveAccordion(id)"
                class="flex items-center justify-between w-full p-4 pb-1 text-left font-medium select-none"
              >
                <span>{word1}</span>
                <svg
                  class="w-5 h-5 duration-300 ease-out text-accent-600 -rotate-[45deg]"
                  :class="{ '-rotate-[45deg]': activeAccordion==id }"
                  xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                  fill="none"
                  viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                  stroke-width="1.5"
                  stroke="currentColor"
                  ><path
                    stroke-linecap="round"
                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                    d="M12 6v12m6-6H6"></path></svg
                >
              </button>
              <div x-show="activeAccordion==id" x-collapse="">
                <div class="p-4 pt-2 text-accent-600">
                  {definition1}
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div
            x-data="{ activeAccordion: '', setActiveAccordion(id) { this.activeAccordion = (this.activeAccordion == id) ? '' : id } }"
            class="relative w-full mx-auto font-normal"
          >
            <div
              x-data="{ id: $id('accordion') }"
              :class="{ 'text-black': activeAccordion==id, 'text-accent-900 hover:text-accent-600': activeAccordion!=id }"
              class="cursor-pointer group text-black"
            >
              <button
                @click="setActiveAccordion(id)"
                class="flex items-center justify-between w-full p-4 pb-1 text-left font-medium select-none"
              >
                <span>{word2}</span>
                <svg
                  class="w-5 h-5 duration-300 ease-out text-accent-600 -rotate-[45deg]"
                  :class="{ '-rotate-[45deg]': activeAccordion==id }"
                  xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                  fill="none"
                  viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                  stroke-width="1.5"
                  stroke="currentColor"
                  ><path
                    stroke-linecap="round"
                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                    d="M12 6v12m6-6H6"></path></svg
                >
              </button>
              <div x-show="activeAccordion==id" x-collapse="">
                <div class="p-4 pt-2 text-accent-600">
                  {definition2}
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div
            x-data="{ activeAccordion: '', setActiveAccordion(id) { this.activeAccordion = (this.activeAccordion == id) ? '' : id } }"
            class="relative w-full mx-auto font-normal"
          >
            <div
              x-data="{ id: $id('accordion') }"
              :class="{ 'text-black': activeAccordion==id, 'text-accent-900 hover:text-accent-600': activeAccordion!=id }"
              class="cursor-pointer group text-black"
            >
              <button
                @click="setActiveAccordion(id)"
                class="flex items-center justify-between w-full p-4 pb-1 text-left font-medium select-none"
              >
                <span>{word3}</span>
                <svg
                  class="w-5 h-5 duration-300 ease-out text-accent-600 -rotate-[45deg]"
                  :class="{ '-rotate-[45deg]': activeAccordion==id }"
                  xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                  fill="none"
                  viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                  stroke-width="1.5"
                  stroke="currentColor"
                  ><path
                    stroke-linecap="round"
                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                    d="M12 6v12m6-6H6"></path></svg
                >
              </button>
              <div x-show="activeAccordion==id" x-collapse="">
                <div class="p-4 pt-2 text-accent-600">
                  {definition3}
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div
            x-data="{ activeAccordion: '', setActiveAccordion(id) { this.activeAccordion = (this.activeAccordion == id) ? '' : id } }"
            class="relative w-full mx-auto font-normal"
          >
            <div
              x-data="{ id: $id('accordion') }"
              :class="{ 'text-black': activeAccordion==id, 'text-accent-900 hover:text-accent-600': activeAccordion!=id }"
              class="cursor-pointer group text-black"
            >
              <button
                @click="setActiveAccordion(id)"
                class="flex items-center justify-between w-full p-4 pb-1 text-left font-medium select-none"
              >
                <span>{word4}</span>
                <svg
                  class="w-5 h-5 duration-300 ease-out text-accent-600 -rotate-[45deg]"
                  :class="{ '-rotate-[45deg]': activeAccordion==id }"
                  xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                  fill="none"
                  viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                  stroke-width="1.5"
                  stroke="currentColor"
                  ><path
                    stroke-linecap="round"
                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                    d="M12 6v12m6-6H6"></path></svg
                >
              </button>
              <div x-show="activeAccordion==id" x-collapse="">
                <div class="p-4 pt-2 text-accent-600">
                  {definition4}
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center">
        <svg
          xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
          class="inline"
          width="20em"
          height="20em"
          viewBox="0 0 32 32"
        >
          <style>
            .word {
              font-size: 3px;
              fill: #ff7a00;
              font-family: "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, sans-serif;
            }
          </style>
          <line
            x1="1"
            y1="2"
            x2="8"
            y2="2"
            stroke="#ff7a00"
            stroke-width="1.5"
            stroke-linecap="round"></line>
          <line
            x1="1"
            y1="7"
            x2="8"
            y2="7"
            stroke="#ff7a00"
            stroke-width="1.5"
            stroke-linecap="round"></line>
          <line
            x1="1"
            y1="12"
            x2="5"
            y2="12"
            stroke="#ff7a00"
            stroke-width="1.5"
            stroke-linecap="round"></line>
          <path
            d="M 3 15 v 11 h 18 m 8 -8 v -16 h -17"
            stroke="#ff7a00"
            stroke-width="1.5"
            fill="none"
            stroke-linecap="round"></path>
          <text class="word" x="11" y="7">{word1.toLocaleLowerCase()}</text>
          <text class="word" x="10" y="12">{word2.toLocaleLowerCase()}</text>
          <text class="word" x="10" y="17">{word3.toLocaleLowerCase()}</text>
          <text class="word" x="11" y="22">{word4.toLocaleLowerCase()}</text>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <div
        x-data="{ activeAccordion: '', setActiveAccordion(id) { this.activeAccordion = (this.activeAccordion == id) ? '' : id } }"
        class="md:col-span-2 md:w-3/4 mx-auto"
      >
        <p
          class="text-2xl tracking-tight text-center font-medium text-black mb-4"
        >
          Story
        </p>
        <div x-data="{ id: $id('accordion') }" class="text-gray-500 text-left">
          <p class="mb-4">
Elias, once hailed as a polymath of remarkable breadth, now found himself trapped in a peculiar carceral state of his own making. The walls were not of stone and steel, but of an overwhelming indolence that seeped into his very bones. The city, with its towering structures and relentless hum, seemed a distant, muted symphony. He’d spent his life dissecting the intricate prosody of language, unraveling the mysteries of mathematics, and even dabbling in the chaotic beauty of theoretical physics. Now, the only rhythm he perceived was the slow, deliberate ticking of the antique clock on his mantle, each tick a tiny hammer blow against the silence he’d cultivated. He’d envisioned retirement as a time of continued exploration, of delving into the uncharted territories of thought. Instead, he was adrift in a sea of ennui, his intellectual sails slack, his compass spinning uselessly.
          </p>
          <div
            @click="setActiveAccordion(id)"
            :class="activeAccordion==id ? 'hidden' : ''"
            class="cursor-pointer text-opacity-70 underline hover:text-accent-900"
          >
            [Continue Reading]
          </div>
          <div x-show="activeAccordion==id" x-collapse="">
            <p>
The old clock tower, a relic of the city’s carceral past, loomed in the distance, a constant reminder of the structures that confined both body and mind. He’d once studied its architecture, marveling at the intricate balance of its design, the way it imposed order upon the chaotic cityscape. Now, it simply served as a stark contrast to his own internal disarray. His garden, a small patch of green rebellion against the concrete jungle, had become his sole sanctuary. The rustling leaves, the chirping crickets, the gentle hum of bees – these were the only prosody he could tolerate, a natural rhythm that soothed his weary soul. He’d traded the complex harmonies of academia for the simple melodies of nature, finding a strange solace in the quiet contemplation of a life lived, and a mind finally at rest.
            </p>
            <div
              @click="setActiveAccordion('')"
              :class="activeAccordion==id ? '' : 'hidden'"
              class="cursor-pointer text-opacity-70 underline hover:text-accent-900 mt-4"
            >
              [Hide]
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
